snippet.title: Nikki & Steven React
snippet.description: What is up Stikkers? Welcome to our channel!!! We are a husband and wife duo, 13+ years strong in the game who LOVES reacting to television shows. Like at home in our daily life, Nikki is the star of the show.  The Walking Dead, The Expanse, Game of Thrones, The Punisher, Cobra Kai and Ozark are some of the shows we’ve come to love. Welcome and enjoy!!!!
